Define CSS in JSX

  ________________________________________________________________________
 |   const customStyle = {                                                |  
 |     backgroundColor: "green",                                          |                    
 |     fontSize: "16px",                                                  |          
 |     padding: "15px 30px",                                              |              
 |     color: "white",                                                    |        
 |     width: "100px",                                                    |          
 |     border: "1px solid #666666",                                       |               
 |     borderRadius: "30px",                                              |                  
 |   };                                                                   |         
 |                                                                        |                       
 |   <button style={customStyle}>+1</button>                              |                  
